  "3130220": {
    "name": "Sagas of Lumin",
    "steam_appid": 3130220,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130220/extras/ac54a368b96e84dfda73ddc1edbf9324.avif?t=1771061953\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130220/extras_big/ac54a368b96e84dfda73ddc1edbf9324.avif?t=1771061953 width=800 height=114 /></span></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130220/extras/185d7f4e61409bfffdbd16c38563937a.poster.avif?t=1771061953\" width=618 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130220/extras/185d7f4e61409bfffdbd16c38563937a.webm?t=1771061953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130220/extras/185d7f4e61409bfffdbd16c38563937a.mp4?t=1771061953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>体验充满生命力的龙类飞行，响应式移动与真实战斗控制相结合。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>这不只是“龙之战”。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>地面战斗强调精准与时机，把近战武器、施法与蒸汽朋克火器结合成一套以技巧为基础的战斗系统。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>玩家可以选择驾驭巨龙从空中进攻，也可落地使用武器与魔法展开近战战斗。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>一个富有剧情的角色扮演游戏，原创世界观设定，你的选择与行为将影响世界的走向与结局。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130220/extras/a9f71ded6678142086d857b6c72b3af0.avif?t=1771061953\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130220/extras_big/a9f71ded6678142086d857b6c72b3af0.avif?t=1771061953 width=800 height=114 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130220/extras/212e4e34457876bcde0c188d9d384b4a.poster.avif?t=1771061953\" width=618 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130220/extras/212e4e34457876bcde0c188d9d384b4a.webm?t=1771061953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130220/extras/212e4e34457876bcde0c188d9d384b4a.mp4?t=1771061953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全面掌控手动飞行：上升、俯冲、悬停与急转，精准应对空中战局。释放火焰吐息并施展近战攻击，例如爪击、撕咬与猛扑，在实时空中战斗中压制敌龙。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130220/extras/9b6cb1ec59962ac7e641fbfbc57a42d6.avif?t=1771061953\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130220/extras_big/9b6cb1ec59962ac7e641fbfbc57a42d6.avif?t=1771061953 width=800 height=114 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130220/extras/9b9e304ecc9002f7f47e769998976a36.poster.avif?t=1771061953\" width=618 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130220/extras/9b9e304ecc9002f7f47e769998976a36.webm?t=1771061953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130220/extras/9b9e304ecc9002f7f47e769998976a36.mp4?t=1771061953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >瞄准飞艇的帆布、引擎与火炮释放火焰，同时躲避可能致命的重型炮火威胁。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130220/extras/e554ffcacda539be92dfdae40934be31.avif?t=1771061953\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130220/extras_big/e554ffcacda539be92dfdae40934be31.avif?t=1771061953 width=800 height=114 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130220/extras/d2a9f402876735512338767501e6799c.poster.avif?t=1771061953\" width=618 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130220/extras/d2a9f402876735512338767501e6799c.webm?t=1771061953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130220/extras/d2a9f402876735512338767501e6799c.mp4?t=1771061953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >释放火焰的野蛮力量摧毁敌方基地，或将敌兵抓上高空让他们感受重力的可怕——同时规避基地防御系统的致命打击。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130220/extras/ef31767a165b813fa6c66ad8c88a4c07.avif?t=1771061953\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130220/extras_big/ef31767a165b813fa6c66ad8c88a4c07.avif?t=1771061953 width=800 height=114 /></span><strong></strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130220/extras/f64da3c4c6da0547dd926789f42b6cc6.poster.avif?t=1771061953\" width=618 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130220/extras/f64da3c4c6da0547dd926789f42b6cc6.webm?t=1771061953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130220/extras/f64da3c4c6da0547dd926789f42b6cc6.mp4?t=1771061953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >地面战斗重视精准与时机，结合剑、斧与长枪等冷兵器，搭配法术与蒸汽朋克火器，构建以技巧为核心的战斗体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130220/extras/d7f5cc6b45caa4f38ae100f2745d40d5.avif?t=1771061953\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130220/extras_big/d7f5cc6b45caa4f38ae100f2745d40d5.avif?t=1771061953 width=800 height=114 /></span></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Sagas of Lumin 拥有一段深刻的叙事，你的每一个决定都能改变结局。这个世界充满道德灰色地带，避免落入传统的善恶二元套路。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong></p>",
